{"tid":1469462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"講個好簡單道理","createTime":"2019-08-14T01:55:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T02:43:34.000Z","uid":53666,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c3657add1c3a579109a032d0bff21929c466ea9c","tid":1469462,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:55:39.000Z","msg":"琴日你阿媽去街市買豬肉, 比豬肉榮呃咗秤, 今日你幫伯母出頭去理論, 會去搵邊個?<br />\n<br />\n緊係去返佢檔口搵豬肉榮啦? 呢啲叫寃有頭債有主。<br />\n你搵埋佢屋企人都仲得。但你無理由 走去搞牛肉強同賣菜華個檔口, 然後同佢哋講, 你要怪就怪豬肉榮啦。<br />\n<br />\n即係咁, <br />\n搞機場, 合理飛一開始話要癱瘓, 令政府蝕入肉同啲國際丟架。<br />\n咁你去搞啲出境遊客有咩用? 你覺得佢哋返到自己祖國會去搵政府投訴?<br />\n<br />\n加埋噚日港共玩陰招比啲機照起飛, 旅客入到閘當佢贏。入唔到當 No-show<br />\n我哋去阻班旅客, 完美咁中晒圈套。<br />\n<br />\n要癱瘓機場, <br />\n必須要人多, 同埋一定要配合罷工。<br />\n<br />\n暫時放低勇武。 集氣再玩鋪大。未嘗不可。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">利申: 合法合情合理, 大家一定要守法啊!!!<br />\n同埋我係嚟支持豬肉榮的。</span></span>"},{"pid":"cbb8a2850518c48b62bec77cb7375e59eb67b5de","tid":1469462,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:03:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ChanKamShui/posts/2384807231606086\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FChanKamShui%2Fposts%2F2384807231606086&d=0oBAxbMcX4V1PEKlHKxm0RSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=101e9b9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ChanKamShui/posts/2384807231606086</a><br />\n<br />\n台灣旅客 8.13 第一身經歷"},{"pid":"1f26af9dba9118bcf933f3715adc166446b2d93c","tid":1469462,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:04:27.000Z","msg":"簡單而言,<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">梁天琦致香港人的信：<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">懇請不要被仇恨支配自己</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/梁天琦致香港人的信/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%A2%81%E5%A4%A9%